<h2>The width and height Properties</h2>
<p>Set the width of the table, and the height of the table header row:</p>

<table onmouseover="bigImg(this)" onmouseout="normalImg(this)" border="0" alt="Smiley" width="80" height="80">
  <script>
function bigImg(x) {
    x.style.height = "64px";
    x.style.width = "64px";
}

function normalImg(x) {
    x.style.height = "32px";
    x.style.width = "32px";
}
</script>

